[30;1m146 | [0m[35mclass TracingBackend(enum.Enum):[0m
[30;1m147 | [0m[35m    '''[0m
[30;1m148 | [0m[35m    Backend type to use for tracing. ``chrome`` uses the Chrome-integrated[0m
[30;1m149 | [0m[35m    tracing service and is supported on all platforms. ``system`` is only[0m
